description: Proactive context compaction at ~50% usage in long Cursor Agent sessions
alwaysApply: true
---

# Context compaction

When the chat context usage indicator appears to be at or above ~50%, pause and tell the user to run `/summarize` before continuing with large tasks.

After summarization (or if the user declines), preserve task state explicitly: current goal, files changed, open TODOs, and next steps.

Do not start unrelated work in the same chat after context has been heavily used; suggest a new chat for unrelated tasks.
